inputs.text: Diverse community members' hands gently tending to a newly planted sapling, captured in a close-up shot within a beautifully restored urban park trail system under clear daylight, with bright, inviting natural light creating a fresh atmosphere, shallow depth of field (85mm, f/2.8) and ample copy space on the right side, featuring an optimistic color palette of natural greens and blues with subtle warm accents, delivering authentic documentary quality with realistic textures and high detail, brand-free environment with generic park elements and clean surfaces.
